rating_comment: Excellent place to stay in Dhaka. Great communication and everything went smoothly. Homely feel on an atmospheric street. The guys working at the apartment took care of my laundry free of charge which was a nice touch.

Rating, 5 stars,  · October 2022,  · Stayed a few nights
rating_comment: Everything about this stay was great. As a tourist, Dhaka isn't the easiest place to arrive into. This Airbnb makes check in as easy as possible by providing a very accurate address as soon as reservation is confirmed, as well as a series of numbers to call for assistance which were all very responsive. I was given apparently the 'small' room, which was still a very good sized room with a double bed. Everything in the flat worked really well, including the Wifi which was very strong. I would definitely stay here again.
